Hi!

Here's a merge of Guillaume's and Rene's lists. I've used Guillaume's list as
base, as I prefer his groupings to Rene's. I havent changed any values, 
just added the cost, talent, adv AV, def. TD and extra skills from Rene's list. 
Where the two differ I've kept Guillaume's values. 

In the comment column I've mentioned what differs on Rene's list. Where there's
an * in comment the skill is added from rene's list.

I have not added those of Rene's skills that we agreed on were not needed for
game testing, and I have not added those skills that I don't think should be
skills (most of the willpower skills, that aught to be spells).

/Per


